a lot of work to go around.

539
00:48:18,508 --> 00:48:20,771
But Emmet even agreed
at that time...

540
00:48:20,843 --> 00:48:23,675
to do a couple of sides
for the Victor label.

541
00:48:23,745 --> 00:48:26,442
He did "Melancholy Baby,"
"Exactly Like You"...

542
00:48:26,514 --> 00:48:28,811
and "I'll See You In My Dreams."

543
00:49:21,100 --> 00:49:23,966
