I can't buy Hattie a birthday present.

623
00:53:59,704 --> 00:54:02,365
You can't buy champagne
if you can only afford beer.

624
00:54:02,439 --> 00:54:04,635
I'm the best guitar player
in the world!

625
00:54:04,709 --> 00:54:07,005
If I want the car,
I should have it.

